&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\tKnock<br />\n\tKnock refers to a hitting or tapping action on a surface. What is knocking? What is being knocked? What is the reason?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They knocked... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) knock before entering a room<br />\n\t2) knock on the blackboard to get the students' attentionn<br />\n\t3) knock over a bottle on the table<br />\n\t4) the engine is knocking<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tOf course, he could not stay down for too long. It would be really awkward if the club manager were to walk in at this time. So, the interior designer picked up his pen and returned to his seat. He checked the time on his watch. The phone call the club manager picked up must be rather important, seeing he had still not yet returned to the office. The designer took a few more sips of his coffee and realized he had almost finished the drink. Just then, there was a slight knock on the door.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/169940497853/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869687/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p869687\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p932266/\">口试改革后，零基础如何通关四六级？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p930357/\">最后25天如何利用真题提分100+ ？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p868552/\">10种缩短运动酸痛期的神奇美食！</a></li><li s